def_cn: 跳歌歌舞的（歌歌舞是一种衣着暴露的女子在夜总会随着流行音乐表演的舞蹈）
def_en: A go-go dancer is a young woman whose job involves dancing to pop music in nightclubs wearing very few clothes.

def_cn: 生意兴隆的；赚大钱的；（公司）迅猛发展的
def_en: A go-go period of time is a time when people make a lot of money and businesses are growing. A go-go company is very energetic and is growing fast.
